== Research Interests
My research focuses on the optimization of power and energy systems, including the following research topics:
- Reliability-oriented planning of offshore wind farm electrical systems, integrating contingency modeling and post-fault network reconfiguration
- Aggregated scheduling of distributed energy resources in distribution systems, incorporating batteries, EVs, and thermal loads under uncertainty

